* /*      REASON CODE.                                               */ 00950002
* /*    . TWO BYTES IN WHICH DYNAMIC ALLOCATION WILL RETURN AN       */ 01000002
* /*      INFORMATIONAL REASON CODE.                                 */ 01050002
* /*    . A FULLWORD CONTAINING THE ADDRESS OF A LIST OF POINTERS TO */ 01100002
